                                <br><br>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-footer">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 instrument-box eq-blocks card">
                        <div class="ins-tr-wrapper card-body">
                            <h4 class="ins-title">Period Converter Indicator</h4>
                            <div class="ins-desc">
                                Connect unsupported and native timeframes in an offline MT4 chart, similarly to the platform’s in-built PeriodConverter, but with continual updates rather than a one-off conversion of the data.

                                <br><br>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-footer">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 instrument-box eq-blocks card">
                        <div class="ins-tr-wrapper card-body">
                            <h4 class="ins-title">Symbol Info Indicator</h4>
                            <div class="ins-desc">
                                A symbol status overview in a draggable sub-window inside your MT4 chart to show price changes, distance from recent highs and lows, and extra indicators that show up and down signals of various timeframes. No limit to the number of copies – the more you want to see, the more you get, in your own combo of settings.
                                <br><br>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-footer">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 instrument-box eq-blocks card">
                        <div class="ins-tr-wrapper card-body">
                            <h4 class="ins-title">Pivot Indicator</h4>
                            <div class="ins-desc">
                                The classic pivot calculation based on historic price, with a twist – 3 support and resistance levels on either side of a central pivot price. Any timeframe goes, and alerts can follow you for rapid reacting to the current price crossing a support or resistance level.

                                <br><br>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-footer">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
